- This looks so good.
- Eat slowly.

35
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:22,360
Don't worry about anything.

36
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:24,630
Got it?

37
00:04:38,030 --> 00:04:40,030
Monk Myung-chul.

38
00:04:43,930 --> 00:04:45,760
I guess he's not here.

39
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:48,030
I guess so.

40
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,700
What did he watch again?

41
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:01,730
Bong-pal, is this you?
You are so cute!

42
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,800
When was it?

43
00:05:05,060 --> 00:05:06,430
Wait, it's the tape
from my graduation.

44
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:08,860
Why was he watching this
out of the blue?

45
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:11,500
He kept mentioning
my graduation earlier.

46
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:21,260
- Come on, let's watch a bit more.
- It's nothing. Forget it.

47
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:23,630
I'm curious about your childhood.

48
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,600
Forget it. Just watch it next time.

49
00:05:25,660 --> 00:05:27,430
When next time?

50
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,230
Just next time.

51
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:32,330
Who recorded this?

52
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,760
Oh, my father.

53
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:37,000
He used to work as
a producer a long time ago.

54
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:39,460
So it must have been a copy of his.

55
00:05:40,430 --> 00:05:43,860
Did your father record all
those videos in that room, too?

56
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,830
Yes.

57
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:49,560
- What did he film?
- I don't know. Random stuff.

58
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:51,230
I've never watched them.

59
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:01,830
But…

60
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:07,500
Why do you live
separately from your dad?

61
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:13,500
It just... ended up like that.
I'm going to wash up.

62
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,330
Okay.

63
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:08,000
There's something
suspicious about that punk.

64
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:15,100
- Is it good?
- It's totally good. Sit down.

65
00:07:16,530 --> 00:07:21,730
- Should we go inside?
- No, it's not cold at all.

66
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:51,760
Goodness, goodness.

67
00:07:53,260 --> 00:07:55,760
Let's turn it off.

68
00:07:56,330 --> 00:07:58,659
- I'm going to bed.
- Oh, yeah.

69
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:01,860
Good night.

70
